I heard that bananas are bad luck on fishing trips.
Me aunt would often tell me of the luck of a four-leafed clover. Imagine what a box of them could do!
Horseshoes are said to be lucky - if you have them the right way up, that is.
Some sailing routes are shorter, but can bring you closer to pirates.
I'll pay more for items if you bring em' from further away.
If you attempt to flee, pirates will stash their loot to catch up. You won't get it, even if you beat them.